{Speech 2}{}{Move along, move along. This is a special operation.@@Leave the area. A special government operation is in progress.@@Don't interfere. Better get out of here. You weren't invited.@@You have exactly 30 seconds to get out of here.@@You're not allowed here. I order you to leave the area immediately.}
